metadata.description: Metagave is the worldâ€™s first community-driven tequila project that uses the power of Web3 technology to allow holders to own some premium tequila and become part of the brand through our DAO. Our aim is to merge the conventional world of physical products and Web2 with the innovative digital landscape of Web3. By blending the physical and digital worlds, we create an unparalleled "Phygital" experience.
